Required software for Web Application
1)tomcat 
2)eclipse java ee(https://www.eclipse.org/downloads/packages/release/2024-12/r)
3)JDK

How to create a web project in eclipse
1)click on file and click on new
2)click on dynamic web project
3)provide project name
4)select tomcat on clicking  new runtime
5)click on next 
6)click on finish

How to deploy the project
1)right click on the project (MyFirstWebProject )
2)select runas >run on server 
3)open the browser
4)provide the URL(http://localhost:8080/MyFirstWebProject/home.html)